	cairo-shlibs (>= 1.6-1),
	libtiff-shlibs,
	giflib-shlibs | libungif-shlibs,
	libexif12-shlibs,
	mono (>= 1.9.1-1),
	mono-tools (>= 1.9-1)
<<
BuildDepends: <<
	atk1 (>= 1.20.0-1),
	cairo (>= 1.6-1),
	expat1,
	fink (>= 0.28.0-1),
	fontconfig2-dev (>= 2.4.1-1),
	freetype219 (>= 2.3.5-1),
	gettext-tools,
	glib2-dev (>= 2.14.0-1),
	glitz (>= 0.4.4-1),
	libexif12,
	libgettext3-dev,
	libiconv-dev,
	libicu36-dev | libicu32-dev,
	libjpeg,
	libpng3,
	libtiff,
	libungif | giflib,
	mono-dev (>= 1.9.1-1),
	pixman (>= 0.10.0-1),
	pkgconfig (>= 0.22-3),
	system-java14-dev,
	x11-dev
<<
Homepage: http://www.mono-project.com/
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <libgdiplus@fink.racoonfink.com>
Description: System.Drawing implementation for Mono
NoSetCPPFLAGS: true
SetCPPFLAGS: -I%p/lib/freetype219/include -I%p/lib/freetype219/include/freetype -I%p/include -I/usr/X11R6/include
NoSETLDFLAGS: true
SetLIBS: -L%p/lib/freetype219/lib -L%p/lib -Wl,-framework,IOKit
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --with-cairo=system --disable-dependency-tracking
CompileScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex

	export PKG_CONFIG_PATH="%p/lib/freetype219/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH"
	export lt_cv_sys_max_cmd_len=65536 PATH="%p/lib/freetype219/bin:$PATH"
	./configure %c
	make
<<
InstallScript: make -j1 install DESTDIR=%d
Shlibs: !%p/lib/libgdiplus.0.dylib
PostInstScript: <<
	[ -x "%p/bin/monodoc" ] && [ -d "%p/lib/monodoc" ] && "%p/bin/monodoc" --make-index >/dev/null 2>&1 || :
<<

DescDetail: <<
libgdiplus is an Open Source implementation of the GDI+ API.
